{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>今日（4日）早上6時02分，元朗公庵路328號一貨倉起火，居民見狀報案求助。消防到場出動2條喉及2隊煙帽隊撲救，火勢於早上6時44分熄滅，疏散約6人。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260504/1127891882903605248698540.jpeg/crBlG1_ZOOOskbJJx-g5oIUDUfmRPhelJc-dJQ_PnSU\" alt=\"消防到場撲救。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>消防到場撲救。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260504/1127891878126161920734956.jpeg/lzlc5wlavc2sEp3f_cCJf58HEGMK1uqconFGsYhxRrE\" alt=\"消防到場出動2條喉及2隊煙帽隊撲救，火勢於早上6時44分熄滅。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>消防到場出動2條喉及2隊煙帽隊撲救，火勢於早上6時44分熄滅。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260504/1127891086929432576572013.jpeg/j02Iq3_nhcaJ_gBmVYGW4pcp8_Qk22mz6RNYysMTWMo\" alt=\"元朗公庵路328號一貨倉有貨櫃起火。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>元朗公庵路328號一貨倉有貨櫃起火。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260504/1127891083758407680260735.jpeg/bbKErxo-Pw3JLM5EKGXcNOoCLXi7q980X0uJRHVLiUQ\" alt=\"消防到場出動2條喉及2隊煙帽隊撲救。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>消防到場出動2條喉及2隊煙帽隊撲救。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260504/1127891875013857280219703.jpeg/2jgyCgYmZVolVJkBwmXV6R9GAR96MALZwhhE6OgYROg\" alt=\"消防到場撲救。（蔡正邦攝）\"><figcaption>消防到場撲救。（蔡正邦攝）</figcaption></figure><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260219/1101161276358266880865023.jpeg/EDiDyzs-GG_dNfDjCfUDDUN0K81saPufP3Y2fD92Nnw\" alt=\"傷者被送往博愛醫院治理。（資料圖片）\"><figcaption>傷者被送往博愛醫院治理。（資料圖片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-05-04T02:06:55.771008+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":210,"images":6,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}